name: semver
description: The semantic version parser used by npm.

repo_metadata.description: The semver parser for node (the one npm uses)

advisories.title: semver vulnerable to Regular Expression Denial of Service
advisories.description: Versions of the package semver before 7.5.2 on the 7.x branch, before 6.3.1 on the 6.x branch, and all other versions before 5.7.2 are vulnerable to Regular Expression Denial of Service (ReDoS) via the function new Range, when untrusted user data is provided as a range.

advisories.title: Regular Expression Denial of Service in semver
advisories.description:
Versions 4.3.1 and earlier of `semver` are affected by a regular expression denial of service vulnerability when extremely long version strings are parsed.



## Recommendation

Update to version 4.3.2 or later
